'''飓风莱恩'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Lane}}）是[[2006年太平洋飓风季|2006年太平洋飓风季]]期间第13个获得命名的[[风暴|风暴]]，第9个飓风以及第6场大型飓风，也是继[[2002年太平洋飓风季|2002年太平洋飓风季]]中的[[2002年飓风肯纳|2002年飓风肯纳]]以来在[[墨西哥|墨西哥]][[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]最强劲的[[太平洋飓风|太平洋飓风]]。莱恩由9月13日墨西哥以南的一股[[东风波|东风波]]发展而成，之后朝西北方向与墨西哥海岸平行移动，并在进入一片有利于其进一步强化的区域后不断增强。向东北转向后，莱恩达到每小时205公里的最高风速，并以最高强度在[[锡那罗亚州|锡那罗亚州]]登陆。9月17日，风暴迅速弱化并消散，之后其残余还给[[美国|美国]][[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]]南部地区带去了降水。

这场飓风共计造成墨西哥境内四人丧生，经济损失超过2亿[[美元|美元]]（2006年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|200000000|2006}}}}美元）。其中以风暴登陆的锡那罗亚州所受损失最为惨重，许多地方电力中断，道路受损，该州农业也受到沉重打击。整个墨西哥有超过4000户家庭、24.8万人受到风暴影响。[[阿卡普尔科|阿卡普尔科]]的道路和机场都遭遇了洪水，一些地区还出现了[[泥石流|泥石流]]。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Lane 2006 track.png}}
2006年8月31日，一股东风波离开[[非洲|非洲]]海岸向西移动，于9月10日进入东[[太平洋|太平洋]]，这一过程中东风波没有获得任何发展<ref name="tcr">{{cite web | author = Richard Knabb | year = 2006 | title = Hurricane Lane Tropical Cyclone Report | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2013-11-22 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-EP132006_Lane.pdf | format = PDF | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2013-05-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130521105827/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-EP132006_Lane.pdf }}</ref>。[[特万特佩克湾|特万特佩克湾]]以南数百[[英里|英里]]外有一片[[对流|大气对流区]]沿东风波轴线发展出来<ref name="sept12two">{{cite report | author = Cobb/Pasch | year = 2006 | title = September 12 Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2006-09-15}}</ref>。天气系统缓慢向西行进<ref name="sept11two">{{cite report | author = Aguirre/Avila | year = 2006 | title = September 11 Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2006-09-15}}</ref>并稳步组织起来<ref name="sept12two2">{{cite web | author = Aguirre/Avila | year = 2006 | title = September 12 Tropical Weather Outlook (2) | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2006-09-15}}</ref>，其中心逐渐发展出对流和[[雨带|带状特征]]，气象部门于9月13日将系统归类为第{{lang|en|13-E}}号热带低气压<ref name="td13disc1">{{cite web | author = Blake/Beven | year = 2006 | title = Tropical Depression Thirteen-E Discussion One | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2013-11-22 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-10-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121017125820/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep13/ep132006.discus.001.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep13/ep132006.discus.001.shtml? }}</ref>。低气压继续组织和强化，于9月14日在距墨西哥海岸约145公里处成为热带风暴，[[国家飓风中心_(美国)|美国国家飓风中心]]因此将其命名为“莱恩”（{{lang|en|Lane}}）。由于风暴上空有可能发展出[[反气旋|反气旋]]，并且行进路径上的水温较高，美国国家飓风中心通过[[热带气旋预报模型|飓风强度预测模型统计]]后认为，莱恩有46%的可能会迅速强化<ref name="lanedisc3">{{cite web | author = Rhome/Knabb | year = 2006 | title = Tropical Storm Lane Discussion Three | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2013-11-22 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep13/ep132006.discus.003.shtml? | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121017125831/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep13/ep132006.discus.003.shtml | archivedate = 2012-10-17 }}</ref>。

[[Image:2006259_1530rgb.jpg|thumb]]
风暴的组织性继续改善，其深层对流发展出[[风眼|中心密集的阴云]]，西半部分也呈现出层次分明的[[外流_(气象)|外流]]<ref name="lanedisc4">{{cite web | author = Beven | year = 2006 | title = Tropical Storm Lane Discussion Four | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2013-11-22 | archivedate = 2012-10-17 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121017125844/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep13/ep132006.discus.004.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep13/ep132006.discus.004.shtml? }}</ref>。9月14日晚，风暴在接近墨西哥海岸线的过程中开始发展出[[风眼|风眼墙]]<ref name="lanedisc5">{{cite web | author = Franklin | year = 2006 | title = Tropical Storm Lane Discussion Five | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2013-11-22 | archivedate = 2012-10-17 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep13/ep132006.discus.005.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121017165459/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep13/ep132006.discus.005.shtml }}</ref>。莱恩在转朝西北偏北方向移动时继续加强，并围绕墨西哥上空的一个中层[[高压脊|高压脊]]转动<ref name="lanedisc7">{{cite web | author = Rhome/Knabb | year = 2006 | title = Tropical Storm Lane Discussion Seven | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2013-11-22 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep13/ep132006.discus.007.shtml? | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121017165515/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep13/ep132006.discus.007.shtml | archivedate = 2012-10-17 }}</ref>。根据[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]][[侦察机|侦察机]]的报告，美国国家飓风中心于9月15日将位于[[哈利斯科州|哈利斯科州]]卡布科连特斯（{{lang|en|Cabo Corrientes}}）西北偏西方向约65公里处的莱恩升级为飓风<ref name="lanedisc9">{{cite web | author = Beven | year = 2006 | title = Hurricane Lane Discussion Nine | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2013-11-22 | archivedate = 2012-10-17 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121017165536/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep13/ep132006.discus.009.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep13/ep132006.discus.009.shtml? }}</ref>。随后风暴还在快速加强，仅6小时后风速就已经达到每小时165公里，达到[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下的二级飓风标准。这天晚上，风暴宽达16公里的风眼从[[玛丽亚群岛|玛丽亚群岛]]掠过<ref name="lanedisc10">{{cite web | author = Roberts/Stewart | year = 2006 | title = Hurricane Lane Discussion Ten | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2013-11-22 | archivedate = 2012-10-17 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep13/ep132006.discus.010.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121017165602/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep13/ep132006.discus.010.shtml }}</ref>。9月16日清晨，飓风在距墨西哥海岸85公里处风速增强到每小时185公里，成为2006年太平洋飓风季的第六场大型飓风<!--Source says fifth major hurricane, which is for Eastern Pacific proper; Hurricane Ioke reached major hurricane status earlier in the season, but in the Central Pacific--><ref name="lane11">{{cite web | author = Rhome/Knabb | year = 2006 | title = Hurricane Lane Discussion Eleven | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2013-11-22 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-10-24 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep13/ep132006.public.011.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121024030433/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep13/ep132006.public.011.shtml }}</ref>。

飓风莱恩还在继续增强，14公里宽的风眼周围由非常强烈的深层对流环绕，风暴在9月16日中午达到风速每小时205公里的最高强度<ref name="lanedisc12">{{cite web | author = Beven | year = 2006 | title = Hurricane Lane Discussion 12 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2013-11-22 | archivedate = 2012-10-17 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121017165614/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep13/ep132006.discus.012.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep13/ep132006.discus.012.shtml? }}</ref>。之后风暴意外转朝东北方向前进，于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]16日晚上19点15分在[[锡那罗亚州|锡那罗亚州]]一片人烟稀少的区域登陆，具体位置在该州埃尔多拉多（{{lang|en|El Dorado}}）东南方向约32公里<ref name="laneupdate">{{cite web | author = Beven | year = 2006 | title = Hurricane Lane Update | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2013-11-22 | archivedate = 2012-10-24 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121024030438/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep13/ep132006.update.09161926.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep13/ep132006.update.09161926.shtml? }}</ref><ref name="oregon">{{cite news | author = Will Weissert | year = 2006 | title = Lane weakens after lashing Mexico coast | publisher = Associated Press | accessdate = 2013-11-22 | work = News Archive | archivedate = 2013-11-22 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131122130515/http://www.apnewsarchive.com/2006/Lane-Weakens-After-Lashing-Mexico-Coast/id-e2345ad552dcf2e98719e0f9141e6c50 | url = http://www.apnewsarchive.com/2006/Lane-Weakens-After-Lashing-Mexico-Coast/id-e2345ad552dcf2e98719e0f9141e6c50 }}</ref>。莱恩因此成为继2002年飓风肯纳后袭击墨西哥的最强飓风<ref name="epachurdat">{{cite web | author = Hurricane Research Division | date = 2010-03-01 | title = Hurricane Data for Pacific Hurricanes 1949–2009 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2010-03-01 | archivedate = 2011-01-03 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/tracks1949to2009_epa.txt | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110103093810/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/tracks1949to2009_epa.txt }}</ref>。墨西哥的山区地形和逐渐加强的西南偏西方向[[风切变|风切变]]共同作用，令风暴强度急剧减弱<ref name="lane14">{{cite web | author = Roberts/Stewart | year = 2006 | title = Hurricane Lane Discussion Fourteen | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2013-11-22 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep13/ep132006.discus.014.shtml? | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121017165627/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep13/ep132006.discus.014.shtml | archivedate = 2012-10-17 }}</ref>，最终于9月17日消散<ref name="lane16">{{cite web | author = Avila | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-10-17 | accessdate = 2013-11-22 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep13/ep132006.discus.016.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | title = Tropical Depression Lane Discussion Sixteen | year = 2006 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121017165703/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep13/ep132006.discus.016.shtml }}</ref>。莱恩的残留之后进入美国[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]]境内<ref name="fbn.com">{{cite web | author = Fortbendnow.com | year = 2006 | title = Fort Bend Under Flood Watch as Storm System Blankets The Region | accessdate = 2007-09-27 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.fortbendnow.com/news/1916/fort-bend-under-flood-watch-as-storm-system-blankets-the-region | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070927080727/http://www.fortbendnow.com/news/1916/fort-bend-under-flood-watch-as-storm-system-blankets-the-region | archivedate = 2007-09-27 }}</ref>。

== 防灾措施 ==
由于莱恩的预计行进路径接近墨西哥西海岸，[[阿卡普尔科|阿卡普尔科]]市相关部门暂时关闭了小型船只的码头<ref name="aplane">{{cite web | author = Associated Press | year = 2006 | title = Tropical Storm Lane lashes Mexico's Pacific coast | accessdate = 2013-11-22 | url = http://www.nbcnews.com/id/14832972/ns/weather/t/tropical-storm-lane-lashes-mexico/ | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2013-11-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131110164618/http://www.nbcnews.com/id/14832972/ns/weather/t/tropical-storm-lane-lashes-mexico/ }}</ref>。几个星期前，[[2006年飓风约翰|飓风约翰]]以一条近似路线经过这一地区，所以一些游客选择提前结束假期搭乘班机回家。许多居民购买了飓风抗灾用品准备应对风暴的袭击。[[格雷罗州|格雷罗州]]的官员还关闭了该州的学校<ref name="lane">{{cite news | author = Will Weissert | year = 2006 | title = Hurricane Lane Heading Toward Baja | publisher = Associated Press | work = AP News Archive | accessdate = 2013-11-22 | archivedate = 2013-11-22 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.apnewsarchive.com/2006/Hurricane-Lane-Heading-Toward-Baja/id-f9db8665818763b1bfdc79e44d15ad6c | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131122140054/http://www.apnewsarchive.com/2006/Hurricane-Lane-Heading-Toward-Baja/id-f9db8665818763b1bfdc79e44d15ad6c }}</ref>。墨西哥沿海地区共计疏散了40400名游客<ref name="ocha">{{cite web | author = United Nations Office for the Coordination of Humanitarian Affairs | year = 2006 | title = Mexico: Hurricane Lane OCHA Situation Report No. 1 | accessdate = 2013-11-22 | archivedate = 2013-11-22 | deadurl = no | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/mexico-hurricane-lane-ocha-situation-report-no-1 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131122140442/http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/mexico-hurricane-lane-ocha-situation-report-no-1 }}</ref>。墨西哥内政部长根据该国民防事务运作部门提供的数据显示，整个墨西哥有21个[[墨西哥行政区划|州]]的550万户[[家庭|家庭]]，共计2100万人受到这场风暴的威胁<ref name="starmedia">{{cite web | author = Servicio Meteorológico Nacional (Mexico) | year = 2006 | title = El huracan 'Lane' crece en la costa oeste del país | accessdate = 2007-09-06 | url = http://mx.starmedia.com/noticias/desastresnaturales/huracanmexico_154914.html | archivedate = 2006-12-15 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20061215191829/http://mx.starmedia.com/noticias/desastresnaturales/huracanmexico_154914.html }}</ref>，政府为此将约2000人疏散到应急避难场所中<ref name="sinal">{{cite web | author = Coordinación General de Asesoria y Políticas Públicas Gobierno del Estato | year = 2006 | title = Sociedad y gobierno unidos ante los daños del Huracán Lane | accessdate = 2013-11-22 | archivedate = 2012-02-18 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120218205620/http://laip.sinaloa.gob.mx/Revistas/CGA/CausaComun/Octubre2006/SOCIEDADYGOBIERNO_UNIDO_HURACAN_LANE.htm | url = http://laip.sinaloa.gob.mx/Revistas/CGA/CausaComun/Octubre2006/SOCIEDADYGOBIERNO_UNIDO_HURACAN_LANE.htm }}</ref>。

随着飓风朝海岸线逼近，从[[米却肯州|米却肯州]]到锡那罗亚州的所有[[港口|海港]]均予以关闭，墨西哥国家气象局向公众警告风暴将带来洪水和[[山崩|山崩]]的威胁。飓风登陆时，锡那罗亚州政府宣布[[自治区_(墨西哥)|自治区]][[阿奥梅|阿奥梅]]、[[瓜萨维_(锡那罗亚州)|瓜萨维]]、安戈斯图拉（{{lang|en|Angostura}}）、萨尔瓦多阿尔瓦拉多（{{lang|en|Salvador Alvarado}}）、[[库利亚坎|库利亚坎]]、[[纳沃拉托_(锡那罗亚州)|纳沃拉托]]、埃罗塔（{{lang|en|Elota}}）、圣伊格纳西奥（{{lang|en|San Ignacio}}）和[[马萨特兰|马萨特兰]]进入[[紧急状态|紧急状态]]<ref name="Esmas landfall">{{cite news |title=Toca tierra el ojo del huracán 'Lane' |publisher=Notimex |author=Staff writer |date=2006-09-16 |accessdate=2013-11-22 |archivedate=2013-11-10 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.esmas.com/noticierostelevisa/mexico/566932.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131110161415/http://www.esmas.com/noticierostelevisa/mexico/566932.html }}</ref>。飓风也导致位于该州马萨特兰的[[拉斐尔·博尔纳将军国际机场|拉斐尔·博尔纳将军国际机场]]多班航班被迫取消<ref name="oregon" />。

[[美国国家气象局|美国国家气象局]]在飓风莱恩的残余进入美国境内以前就向德克萨斯州大部分地区发布了洪水观察预警<ref name="fbn.com" />。

== 冲击 ==
{{Most intense landfalling Pacific hurricanes}}
[[Image:Hurricane_Lane_16_sept_2006_aqua.jpg|thumb]]
风暴给阿卡普尔科带去了暴雨和巨浪，该市沿海街道上的积水达到405毫米深。暴雨导致200户家宅被淹，并引发[[泥石流|泥石流]]，导致一位年仅7岁的男孩遇难。阿卡普尔科的机场也出现了洪水，不过航运没有中断。风暴产生的大浪令一艘船只倾覆，导致一人失踪。[[拉萨罗卡德纳斯|拉萨罗卡德纳斯]]港所降暴雨令运河洪水泛滥，超过500人被迫从家中撤离<ref name="lane" />。米却肯州有占地两平方公里的农作物被毁。[[科利马州|科利马州]]的道路和机场共计受到了价值约3000万[[墨西哥比索|墨西哥比索]]的损失（2006年墨西哥比索，相同于270万2006年[[美元|美元]]和{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|2700000|2006}}}}{{#time:Y}}年美元））<ref name="ocha" />。哈利斯科州的卡洪·德·培尼亚（{{lang|es|Cajón de Peña}}）降雨量共计达到187毫米<ref name="lanepa12a">{{cite web | author = Beven | year = 2006 | title = Hurricane Lane Public Advisory 12A | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2013-11-22 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep13/ep132006.public_a.012.shtml? | archivedate = 2012-10-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121024030451/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep13/ep132006.public_a.012.shtml }}</ref>。一名男子被强风吹得摔倒在地后不治身亡<ref name="landam">{{cite web | author = Tomas Sarmiento | year = 2006 | title = Hurricane Lane leaves destruction in Mexico | publisher = Reuters | accessdate = 2013-11-22 | archivedate = 2013-11-22 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131122150213/http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/hurricane-lane-leaves-destruction-mexico | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/hurricane-lane-leaves-destruction-mexico }}</ref>。整个哈利斯科州一共有109人因山崩和暴雨而被迫离开家园<ref name="bloomberg">{{cite news | author = Margot Habiby | title = Lane Strengthens to Hurricane on Approach to Mexico | publisher = Bloomberg.com | accessdate = 2013-11-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121102071256/http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=newsarchive&sid=am6EHwLzZzuI&refer=latin_america | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-11-02 | date = 2006-09-15 | url = http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=newsarchive&sid=am6EHwLzZzuI&refer=latin_america }}</ref>。

风暴在接近锡那罗亚州埃尔多拉多的地点登陆，导致多条道路和许多单薄的民宅被毁。狂风刮倒了电力塔、树木和交通标志，还令许多地区停电<ref name="landam" />。飓风登岸点东南方向的马萨特兰遭受了狂风暴雨，导致街道被淹，电力中断<ref name="oregon" />。飓风的威胁还迫使一次[[多洛雷斯呼声|独立日游行]]被迫取消<ref name="bbc">{{cite news | author = AP | title = Hurricane Lane hits Mexico coast | accessdate = 2013-11-22 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121107122120/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/5351126.stm | archivedate = 2012-11-07 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/5351126.stm | work = BBC News | date = 2006-09-17 }}</ref>。莱恩还摧毁了马萨特兰到该州首府[[库利亚坎|库利亚坎]]之间的一座桥梁，困住了数十辆卡车。库利亚坎有一人因车冲进了河里而遇难，多条街道被水淹没<ref name="landam" />。整个锡那罗亚州有多条道路受损，许多社区失去了与外界的联系。莱恩还导致该州[[农业|农业]]受到沉重打击，经济损失可能高达6亿墨西哥比索（相当于5500万2006年美元和{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|55000000|2006}}}}{{#time:Y}}年美元）。风暴破坏了多个社区的污水处理设施和分配系统，为此该国卫生部长宣布锡那罗亚州进入卫生警戒状态<ref name="ochs2">{{cite web | author = United Nations Office for the Coordination of Humanitarian Affairs | year = 2006 | title = Mexico: Hurricane Lane OCHA Situation Report No. 2 | accessdate = 2013-11-22 | archivedate = 2013-11-22 | deadurl = no | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/mexico-hurricane-lane-ocha-situation-report-no-2 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131122152411/http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/mexico-hurricane-lane-ocha-situation-report-no-2 }}</ref>。锡那罗亚州遭受的经济损失共计达到约12亿墨西哥比索（相当于1.093亿2006年美元和{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|109300000|2006}}}}{{#time:Y}}年美元）<ref name="sinaloadamagetotal">{{cite news | author = Valdez Cardenas, Javier and Leon, Raymundo | date = 2006-09-24 | title = En Sinaloa, los daños por Lane suman 1,200 millones de pesos | work = La Jornada | accessdate = 2013-11-22 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.jornada.unam.mx/2006/09/24/index.php?section=estados&article=031n3est | archivedate = 2012-10-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121004213812/http://www.jornada.unam.mx/2006/09/24/index.php?section=estados&article=031n3est }}</ref>。

飓风莱恩一共导致墨西哥有4人死亡<ref name="ochs2" />，估计有4320户民房和24.8万人受到影响。有九个自治区的供水系统受损，数千人失去[[自来水|自来水]]供应。共计有3万公里道路或[[高速公路|高速公路]]受到一定程度的破坏，还有一些桥梁被毁。飓风共计给该国造成了约22亿墨西哥比索的损失（相当于2.03亿2006年美元和{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|203000000|2006}}}}{{#time:Y}}年美元）<ref name="sinal" />。此外，莱恩的残余还给美国德克萨斯州南部带去了降雨<ref>{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | year = 2006 | title = 2006 Tropical Weather Summary | accessdate = 2013-11-22 | archivedate = 2013-05-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130521123013/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/tws/MIATWSEP_nov.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/tws/MIATWSEP_nov.shtml? }}</ref>。

== 善后 ==
飓风莱恩登陆次日，之前疏散的居民中大部分开始返回家中进行清理。一些留在当地的游客继续度假，还有一些选择离开<ref name="laftermath">{{cite web |author=Will Weissert |year=1994 |title=Cleaning up, clearing out after Lane |publisher=AP |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2012-10-10 |archivedate=2012-10-10 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121010102834/http://www.cleveland.com/news/plaindealer/index.ssf?%2Fbase%2Fnews%2F1158579059150550.xml&coll=2 |url=http://www.cleveland.com/news/plaindealer/index.ssf?/base/news/1158579059150550.xml&coll=2 }}</ref>。墨西哥联邦政府宣布锡那罗亚州的九个自治区进入紧急状态，由此可以让受到影响的居民获得紧急救灾资金援助<ref name="ocha" />。政府还动用了[[直升机|直升机]]来分发食品并救出被困的居民，并在马萨特兰设立了三个临时避难所，安置了360人，还在库利亚坎设立了另外三个避难所，安置了约1000位灾民<ref name="ochs2" />。为了防止[[登革热|登革热]]的蔓延，政府向67个社区派去了[[流行病学|流行病专家]]，并配有18个移动治疗组和15个喷雾防治组。风暴过去一个月后，所有受到影响的道路和高速公路都已经恢复通车<ref name="sinal" />。

